    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and will require significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across most surfaces. The interior has seen heavy use, with torn upholstery and several non-functioning electronic components, including the radio and air conditioning.",
